SELECT DISTINCT
	r.ClassificationCode AS [ProviderKey],
	r.ClassificationCode AS [Code]
FROM
	@Schema.CustomTable r 

	INNER JOIN dbo.ClassificationType b_classificati ON b_classificati.Name = N'Product Type' AND b_classificati.ProviderId = @ProviderId

WHERE
	r.Record_ImportId = @ImportId
	AND r.Record_HasError = 0

SELECT DISTINCT
	b_classificati.Id AS [ClassificationId],
	b_company.Id AS [CompanyId],
	b_couponfreque.Id AS [CouponFrequencyId],
	b_currency.Id AS [CurrencyId],
	b_curve.Id AS [CurveId],
	b_customattrib.Id AS [CustomAttributeId],
	b_delaytype.Id AS [DelayTypeId],
	b_instrument.Id AS [InstrumentId],
	b_instrumentty.Id AS [InstrumentTypeId],
	b_interesttype.Id AS [InterestTypeId],
	b_listing.Id AS [ListingId],
	b_region.Id AS [RegionId],
	b_seniority.Id AS [SeniorityId]
FROM
	@Schema.CustomTable r 

	INNER JOIN dbo.Classification b_classificati ON b_classificati.ProviderKey = r.ClassificationCode AND b_classificati.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.Company b_company ON b_company.ProviderKey = r.CompanySymbol AND b_company.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.CouponFrequency b_couponfreque ON b_couponfreque.ProviderKey = r.FrequencyCode AND b_couponfreque.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.Currency b_currency ON b_currency.ProviderKey = r.CurrencyCode AND b_currency.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.Curve b_curve ON b_curve.ProviderKey = r.PrimaryIssuerCurve AND b_curve.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.CustomAttribute b_customattrib ON b_customattrib.ProviderKey = r.IsinFuel1 AND b_customattrib.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.DelayType b_delaytype ON b_delaytype.ProviderKey = r.DelayTypeCode AND b_delaytype.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.Instrument b_instrument ON b_instrument.ProviderKey = r.Isin AND b_instrument.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.InstrumentType b_instrumentty ON b_instrumentty.ProviderKey = r.InstrumentTypeName AND b_instrumentty.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.InterestType b_interesttype ON b_interesttype.ProviderKey = r.InterestTypeName AND b_interesttype.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.Listing b_listing ON b_listing.ProviderKey = r.BenchmarkName AND b_listing.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.Region b_region ON b_region.ProviderKey = r.RegionName AND b_region.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.Seniority b_seniority ON b_seniority.ProviderKey = r.SeniorityCode AND b_seniority.ProviderId = @ProviderId

WHERE
	r.Record_ImportId = @ImportId
	AND r.Record_HasError = 0
